text_question_merge: Sib koom ua ke bookmarks tam sim no nrog cov ntawv thov txawv teb lossis hloov lawv?

text_help_content1: Bookmark Manager yog ib daim ntawv thov uas pab khaws thiab kho cov cim hauv internet.
text_help_content2: Txhawm rau tsim phau ntawv tshiab, lossis lub nplaub tshev tshiab, nias lub cim "ntxiv": xaiv ntawm phau ntawv cim npe thiab nplaub tshev, ntxig cov npe thiab thaum kawg qhov URL, tom qab ntawd nias txuag kom txuag tau qhov kev hloov pauv, lossis nias rho tawm kom rho tawm bookmark, lossis rov qab kom hla ntawm cov kev hloov tab sis khaws cov bookmark.
text_help_content3: Nias lub khawm "qhib" nyob ze rau ntawm lub bookmark los qhib URL uas cuam tshuam.
text_help_content4: Nias lub "Ntxiv" khawm nyob rau hauv daim nplaub tshev los ntxiv cov khoom tshiab rau nws.
text_help_content5: Rau ntawm ob qho ntawv cim thiab ntawv tais ceev tseg, nias lub pob "hloov" los hloov lawv, nias "txav mus rov qab" khawm los pauv txoj haujlwm nrog lub hauv ntej dhau los, nias "txav mus rau tom ntej" khawm los pauv txoj haujlwm nrog lub hauv ntej tom ntej, nias lub "txav mus rau sab saum toj" khawm kom txav lub ntsiab lus tawm ntawm daim nplaub tshev qhov chaw nws tam sim no, lossis nias lub pob "txav mus sab hauv" kom txav cov khoom hauv lub subfolder tom ntej.
text_help_content6: Hauv cov ntawv qhia zaub mov, siv tau tom qab txhaj rau "icon" icon, koj tuaj yeem nkaum lossis qhia cov hloov kho, txav thiab ntxiv khawm. Nws tseem tuaj yeem hloov cov lus ntawm tus neeg siv interface.
text_help_content7: Txhawm rau kev lag luam tawm los yog xa tawm ntawm phau ntawv xaiv, nias rau ntawm lub txawv teb / export icon. Cov HTML Netscape Bookmarks hom yog txaus siab, yog li nws tuaj yeem nkag tau qhov Bookmark exported los ntawm lub web browsers loj. Thaum import cov bookmarks los ntawm ib cov ntaub ntawv, cov bookmarks tam sim no yuav raug muab tshem tawm thiab rov muab sau dua.
text_help_content8: Bookmarks Manager yog Progressive Web Application, uas txhais tau tias nws khiav hauv browser. Thaum koj nruab nws, thaum lub browser sib txuas tsis qhia, nws tseem khiav hauv browser. Cov phau ntawv ceev tseg tau muab ceev tseg hauv browser ntawm localStorage rau lub chaw cim bookmarks.marcoparrone.com. localStorage ua haujlwm zoo nrog Chrome, Ntug thiab Firefox browsers. Lwm yam browsers yuav rho tawm localStorage tom qab qee lub sijhawm. Android los ntawm lub neej ntawd siv Chrome, Windows los ntawm lub neej ntawd siv Ntug. Bookmarks Manager tam sim no tsis txaus siab ntawm Apple cov khoom. Nrog lub hom phiaj pab txhawm rau tiv thaiv qhov poob ntawm cov ntawv, nws tau hais kom ua thaub qab siv qhov "export" ua haujlwm, txhua zaus koj ua qee yam kev hloov kho uas koj tsis xav plam.

text_about_content5: Lub vev xaib no tau muab txhais rau koj kom yooj yim siv cov software software uas siv los ntawm Google Translate. Kev sim ua qhov tsim nyog tau muab kev txhais lus kom raug, txawm li cas los xij, tsis muaj kev txhais lus txhais tau zoo yog qhov tsis zoo thiab nws tsis yog los hloov neeg txhais lus.
